<p><span style="white-space:nowrap">Ongjin Peninsula&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><b><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Uijeongbu" title="Battle of Uijeongbu">Uijeongbu</a></b>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">Munsan&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=First_Battle_of_Seoul&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="First Battle of Seoul (page does not exist)">1st Seoul</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">Chuncheon/Hongcheon&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">Gangneung&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">Miari&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">Han River&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Action_of_2_July_1950" title="Action of 2 July 1950">Chumonchin Chan</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Osan" title="Battle of Osan">Osan</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">Donglakri&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">Danyang&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">Jincheon&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap">Yihwaryeong&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Daejeon" title="Battle of Daejeon">Daejeon</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><b><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Pusan_Perimeter" title="Battle of Pusan Perimeter">Pusan Perimeter</a></b>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><b><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Incheon" title="Battle of Incheon">Incheon</a></b>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Inchon#Battle_of_Seoul" title="Battle of Inchon" class="mw-redirect">2nd Seoul</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Hill_282" title="Battle of Hill 282">Hill 282</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowra