i/Battle_of_Pork_Chop_Hill" title="Battle of Pork Chop Hill">Pork Chop Hill</a></b>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Outpost_Harry" title="Outpost Harry">Outpost Harry</a></span></p>
